    <Folder>
      <name>Shopping Guide 血拼指南</name>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Uma and Leopold</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z62ILjId_A8"><img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/z62ILjId_A8/hqdefault.jpg" height="200" width="auto" /></a><br><br><a href="https://www.youtube.com/embed/z62ILjId_A8">https://www.youtube.com/embed/z62ILjId_A8</a><br><br>Uma and Leopold 擁有美麗的印花、柔美的廓形和優質的材料，是島上熱帶衣櫥的最愛。 包括 Seminyak 和 Canggu 在內的全島都有商店，每家精品店都擁有涼爽和輕鬆的氛圍，為您帶來愉快的購物體驗。]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1684-7CB342</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value>https://www.youtube.com/embed/z62ILjId_A8</value>
          </Data>
        </ExtendedData>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            115.1575055,-8.6831416,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Gooseberry Intimates</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4GzYL9r1uGJ3DC8wTdwstV-KGt9i9TjOeJoUYul6JAYMq_8VQDNROl1ZC4pouSILwIesRaeLNSZLkKgd2WHWVMOnnCz7m7WhVh9ha2T5sbsJkcOVEW_qgy4J1vSOHAiFbkhcI7GjXNHMCluTd8B4BLUHvHxXaQgX4DTCR2OSEQYrFZQ04yBrMTaa_6UbOYCiJMrz6N1Oyd?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Gooseberry Intimates 是峇里島上最著名的品牌之一，銷售精緻漂亮的內衣和舒適的泳裝。 他們的商店坐落在繁華的Kayu Aya大街上，乾淨別緻的風格使購物變得輕鬆。 尋找令人難以置信的蕾絲內衣和令人驚嘆的泳裝，讓您充滿自信]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1684-7CB342</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X4GzYL9r1uGJ3DC8wTdwstV-KGt9i9TjOeJoUYul6JAYMq_8VQDNROl1ZC4pouSILwIesRaeLNSZLkKgd2WHWVMOnnCz7m7WhVh9ha2T5sbsJkcOVEW_qgy4J1vSOHAiFbkhcI7GjXNHMCluTd8B4BLUHvHxXaQgX4DTCR2OSEQYrFZQ04yBrMTaa_6UbOYCiJMrz6N1Oyd?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
          </Data>
        </ExtendedData>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            115.1629477,-8.6839512,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Bamboo Blonde</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=UffZBofLZDo"><img src="https://img.youtube.com/vi/UffZBofLZDo/hqdefault.jpg" height="200" width="auto" /></a><br><br><a href="https://www.youtube.com/embed/UffZBofLZDo">https://www.youtube.com/embed/UffZBofLZDo</a><br><br>Bamboo Blonde 坐落在巴厘島的所有主要商業區，是舒適飄逸連衣裙和別緻晚裝的島上主打品牌。 它以合理的價格提供適合各種場合的一切。 Bamboo Blonde 以熱帶圖案、輕質材料和活潑的風格為特色，是熱帶島嶼衣櫥的必備單品。]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1684-7CB342</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value>https://www.youtube.com/embed/UffZBofLZDo</value>
          </Data>
        </ExtendedData>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            115.1400248,-8.6599474,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Niconico Swimwear Oceano</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X71z0xghmFgAhXwET2HZgfKMOQpLx3OqbJUuJYUYiz6aRoTfv8aq1_U8h-oKkhpfkV8yN-_eRF1i4J-6P-3vwERCdKETlAdt0pUB_wkP-3bxEnY5IVkf-3BZg8_ZY0NtGWKSgZNL63-zUsMiqr7d9rJVxLoVvZwPtvnhHxZPDtSSFMfIA0E9SuUtm5HmpqeFM5VnNJtony8?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Nico Nico 是巴厘島創立的泳裝系列，適合各種尺碼。 該品牌的款式迎合季節潮流和島上明媚的晴天，現已涉足度假裝，為在海灘度過一天后遮掩肌膚。 Nico Nico 採用鮮豔的色彩、獨特的圖案和有趣的形狀設計，是巴厘島人的最愛。]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1684-7CB342</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X71z0xghmFgAhXwET2HZgfKMOQpLx3OqbJUuJYUYiz6aRoTfv8aq1_U8h-oKkhpfkV8yN-_eRF1i4J-6P-3vwERCdKETlAdt0pUB_wkP-3bxEnY5IVkf-3BZg8_ZY0NtGWKSgZNL63-zUsMiqr7d9rJVxLoVvZwPtvnhHxZPDtSSFMfIA0E9SuUtm5HmpqeFM5VnNJtony8?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
          </Data>
        </ExtendedData>
        <Point>
          <coordinates>
            115.1608597,-8.6842161,0
          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>The Bali Tailor</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5CshW8ilFBzPcc5vrqhEV2SkYvylzNKfY4rNpBVusP3sJzr6tk83rykib45k7zvwsKdvvjHsm9PrbGKH-G5e_GV37JkkIEXsos5RHJ1a5a2AHqjA_6viMYqkQhds_JGe7uXJJXnDB2ufqTxltm-48Q8rwjRjv3Ah4c3iV5h90jhMjJvJWJtk3CSPmoxpY2OWQqVdl-aTZQ?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>在尋找可以穿一輩子的別緻時尚服裝時，The Bali Tailor 是必去之地。 每件單品均採用優質材料，既耐穿又美觀，營造出輕鬆的島嶼風格。 提供量身定制的白襯衫、連衣裙和鞋子，它們擁有您想要的時尚海島度假所需的一切。]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1684-7CB342</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5CshW8ilFBzPcc5vrqhEV2SkYvylzNKfY4rNpBVusP3sJzr6tk83rykib45k7zvwsKdvvjHsm9PrbGKH-G5e_GV37JkkIEXsos5RHJ1a5a2AHqjA_6viMYqkQhds_JGe7uXJJXnDB2ufqTxltm-48Q8rwjRjv3Ah4c3iV5h90jhMjJvJWJtk3CSPmoxpY2OWQqVdl-aTZQ?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
          </Data>
        </ExtendedData>
