          </coordinates>
        </Point>
      </Placemark>
      <Placemark>
        <name>Bali Boat Shed</name>
        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5U22GAdvc7XcYAwItOo_8gx5NzY9HrHAk_Ux-GaluolHl0rKi12sa-iY-mpZQlVXSYEowYMB5VDQxNH_lrBcgES_mIWnlwHQMEOXwtBhRSZixFlcm4Eyf7TgaCGEAunvHQTWUJy8JNgTiTEdcTwrZs2T3bevGSq3spvbILtNLzqJeayUUWbMtiwtm4PSCG7Em0zr2tJAp_?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>Bali Boat Shed 擁有許多小品牌，提供從裙子到連衣裙和男士必需品的島上基本商品。 憑藉明亮的圖案、塊狀顏色和配飾，您可以穿著打扮或只是在一些舒適的休閒用品中閒逛。 在水明漾的中心地帶，這是一個停下來為您的島嶼衣櫥挑選新衣服的好地方。<br><br><img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5emvueeuTXI0Tq_uPVW5bB4IEAVyEpdMOFD9OxHdTQ_w_ZZ3KDqMcs3qSZHkcwQXx4CBdVkrDk33WXCIhe2xnEZI0VvaANNeitd1R5V3-ZqgarIqPhPgQl7EXzmHcH9Tu0nvDcm-iNC0QzAK6lJsrtaAY5yHJY_zRfkQgIT3qPLk5Es4-DuaeoD3Zgz6ptmeSX96w1c13D?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" />]]></description>
        <styleUrl>#icon-1684-7CB342</styleUrl>
        <ExtendedData>
          <Data name="gx_media_links">
            <value><![CDATA[https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5U22GAdvc7XcYAwItOo_8gx5NzY9HrHAk_Ux-GaluolHl0rKi12sa-iY-mpZQlVXSYEowYMB5VDQxNH_lrBcgES_mIWnlwHQMEOXwtBhRSZixFlcm4Eyf7TgaCGEAunvHQTWUJy8JNgTiTEdcTwrZs2T3bevGSq3spvbILtNLzqJeayUUWbMtiwtm4PSCG7Em0zr2tJAp_?authuser=0&fife=s16383 https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X5emvueeuTXI0Tq_uPVW5bB4IEAVyEpdMOFD9OxHdTQ_w_ZZ3KDqMcs3qSZHkcwQXx4CBdVkrDk33WXCIhe2xnEZI0VvaANNeitd1R5V3-ZqgarIqPhPgQl7EXzmHcH9Tu0nvDcm-iNC0QzAK6lJsrtaAY5yHJY_zRfkQgIT3qPLk5Es4-DuaeoD3Zgz6ptmeSX96w1c13D?authuser=0&fife=s16383]]></value>
