        <description><![CDATA[<img src="https://mymaps.usercontent.google.com/hostedimage/m/*/3AL_Y2X7cFYFX9d3CzRCbUezzRRHjP78_6M685mOaLM8pWzGqHXBIlOC3d1GKLUceMe6xhM_DoIOLP0m8UKjNn1GGjUEWVOoOG2icmFEIMMu32JSrbK7SU2Wd-XqNZXFphy6Z8pcQP0wOs194BwclBY5PuUUD1uiPD4YRoIIn1R5GMInlbYrO3yYKjsagmRxseKDleZ_l-0zDwoEznPlPGNqwzomgiPHqZ9IlBfAnvnNZu5k_N1tlLP50Sktuiik?authuser=0&fife=s16383" height="200" width="auto" /><br><br>说明: 位於水明漾的熱門露天頂樓餐廳，結合悠閒的波西米亞風與熱帶氛圍，主打健康輕食、創意早午餐和特色調酒。菜單包含新鮮沙拉、酪梨吐司、印尼風味料理等，適合白天享用陽光早午餐或傍晚欣賞日落。現場常有DJ音樂，營造輕鬆愉悅的度假氛圍，是當地潮人與遊客的聚集地。<br>名稱: <br>說明: ]]></description>
